2. BURSA MALAYSIA COMPLIANCE (Bursa Malaysia 合规条款)

   (a) All data scraped by this software originates from publicly
       accessible pages of Bursa Malaysia (https://www.bursamalaysia.com/).
       This project does NOT claim ownership of any such data.

   (b) Users must comply with Bursa Malaysia's Terms of Use, data
       policies, and any applicable regulations at all times.

   (c) TAKE-DOWN COMPLIANCE: If Bursa Malaysia issues a take-down
       request, cease-and-desist notice, or any formal objection
       regarding the use of this software or the data it collects,
       the author and all users SHALL:
       - Immediately cease all scraping activities directed at
         Bursa Malaysia's systems upon receipt of such notice;
       - Remove or disable the offending functionality within a
         reasonable timeframe (not exceeding 7 calendar days);
       - Cooperate in good faith with Bursa Malaysia to resolve
         the matter.

   (d) Users who redistribute or deploy this software are
       independently responsible for ensuring their own compliance
       with Bursa Malaysia's policies. The original author shall
       not be held liable for third-party non-compliance.

3. DATA USE RESTRICTIONS (数据使用限制)

   (a) Data obtained through this software SHALL NOT be commercially
       redistributed, resold, or used as a data source for any paid
       product or service, unless the user has obtained explicit
       authorization from Bursa Malaysia.

   (b) Data provided by this software does NOT constitute investment
       advice. The author makes no warranty regarding the accuracy,
