       decisions made based on this data are at the user's own risk.

4. RESPONSIBLE SCRAPING (负责任的抓取行为)

   (a) Users SHALL NOT reduce the default scraping interval below
       the configured 5-minute minimum or initiate excessive
       concurrent requests that may burden the target servers.

   (b) Users SHALL respect the target site's robots.txt directives
       and server capacity limitations.

   (c) Using this software to conduct denial-of-service (DoS)
       attacks or to circumvent access restrictions is STRICTLY
